Package command

Class UnmarkCommand

  • java.lang.Object
    • command.Command
      • command.UnmarkCommand
  • public class UnmarkCommand
extends Command
    The `UnmarkCommand` class represents a command to unmark a task as completed in the BloopBot application. It extends the `Command` class and is responsible for executing the unmark operation. This class takes a task index as input and marks the corresponding task as not completed.
    Version:
    0.0.0
    Author:
    raydenlim
